name: Wild Country Helium 3 Quickdraw (6 pack)
description: A set of 6 lightweight quickdraws, with slim gates and snag-free noses for routes where every gram counts. Slung on superlight Dyneema® they're a great option for long trad routes that call for big racks and multiples of all sizes.Rope-end carabiner is red anodized.Super-strong I-beam back construction keeps the Helium carabiners light.Hooded nose protects gates from rubbing open.Vice plastic sheath holds the bottom carabiner in place for swift clipping.Includes 6 quickdraws.
